quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  74,1,"O you who covers himself [with a garment],{1}",footnotes:1:1
  74,2,"Arise and warn."
  74,3,"And your Lord glorify."
  74,4,"And your clothing purify."
  74,5,"And uncleanliness{1} avoid.",footnotes:1:1
  74,6,"And do not confer favor to acquire more{1}.",footnotes:1:1
  74,7,"But for your Lord be patient."
  74,8,"And when the trumpet is blown,"
  74,9,"That Day will be a difficult day"
  74,10,"For the disbelievers - not easy."